    <description>Electra Cars is an OEM with a premium vehicle website. Long forms cause drop-off. This agent automates test drive booking with Agentforce. It runs a natural chat on web or WhatsApp. It collects vehicle model, preferred date and time, and zip code. It confirms details before saving. It creates Automotive Cloud test drive and related records. It routes the prospect to the right dealership by zip. It sends confirmation on the preferred channel. It improves conversion and data accuracy. It cuts manual follow-up for the call center.</description>
